@{b}CLChatGUI@{ub} is a MUI application.  MUI is (C) 1993-96 Stefan Stuntz.

@{b}AmiTCP@{ub} is (C) 1994-1995 NSDI Inc.

Please send bug-reports, suggestions and comments via E-Mail to
@{b}owagner@lsd.wupper.de@{ub}.

Updates are placed on @{b}AmiNet@{ub}; they can also be downloaded via anonymous
FTP directly from @{b}ftp.vapor.com@{ub}.  You can also check out anonymous FTP
at the servers listed in the @{"ARCnet" Link "ARCnet"} reference if they have a better
link to your host.


