History
*******

@{b}Version 1.7@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed a bug where small windows caused the the line formatter
          to loop infinitely

        @{b}*@{ub} added @{b}/SERVERS@{ub} command to server command menu

        @{b}*@{ub} default setting was saved to @{b}ENVARC@{ub} only, so attempting to
          load defaults without quitting caused the old defaults from
          @{b}ENV@{ub} to be read in

@{b}Version 2.0@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} added CLFT file transfer capability

        @{b}*@{ub} added @{b}/USERS S@{ub} command to server command menu

        @{b}*@{ub} miscellaneous internal fixes & cleanup work

        @{b}*@{ub} now @{b}TCPMode@{ub} can be used as a workbench icon tooltype, too

@{b}Version 2.1@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} scroller now does not jump to the bottom when new entries are
          appended if it not already was there.

        @{b}*@{ub} smoothed out removing of lines in the main listview.

        @{b}*@{ub} added @{b}PING@{ub} option to test round trip time to another user.
          Note that his works with the GUI client only!

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed workbench startup bug: always attempted to load the
          executable itself as a settings file thus ignoring any
          default settings in @{b}ENV:@{ub}.

        @{b}*@{ub} added new option @{b}Auto Reconnect@{ub} to automatically attempt to
          reconnect if the server connections breaks down.

        @{b}*@{ub} nick changes are now tracked and correspondending dialog
          windows are updated with the new nickname

        @{b}*@{ub} changed ping frequency back to 15s to reduce IP load

        @{b}*@{ub} miscellaneous internal fixes & cleanup work

@{b}Version 2.2 (internal)@{ub}
@{b}Version 2.3@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} smoothed out scroller handling a bit; will now jump to the
          bottom on window resizes, and will jump as long as no more
          than two lines are scrolled up

        @{b}*@{ub} file transfer tasks now run with priority 1 for maximum
          performance

        @{b}*@{ub} added better icon created by `NEUMANN'

        @{b}*@{ub} minor speedup in listview display hook

        @{b}*@{ub} added missing cycle chain for option window

@{b}Version 2.4@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} now activating any output window automatically actives the
          correspondending input string gadget

@{b}Version 2.5@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} fixed bug with lines > 255 chars to be corrupted upon listview
          insertion

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed several types in texts

        @{b}*@{ub} now file transfer can be initiated by dropping icons onto a
          dialog window

        @{b}*@{ub} will no longer change topic string gadget contents while user
          is editing it

@{b}Version 2.6 (internal)@{ub}
@{b}Version 2.7 (internal)@{ub}
@{b}Version 2.8@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} changed prefix entries to be more clearly

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed several hidden internal race conditions regarding CLFT
          cleanup which could case enf-hits or visits to india

        @{b}*@{ub} option window is now a register group

        @{b}*@{ub} added CLFT auto receive option

        @{b}*@{ub} added logging capability

        @{b}*@{ub} added PING and SEND FILE buttons to the user dialog windows

        @{b}*@{ub} it is now possible to enter commands in the user dialog
          windows

        @{b}*@{ub} added server history feature

        @{b}*@{ub} added AWAY feature

        @{b}*@{ub} added AWAY, BACK and KICK message configurability

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed topic gadget to always update when the window is
          deactivated even if it is the active object

@{b}Version 2.9@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} changed "««" within dialog window to "IN"

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed various problems with dialog window listview handling
          (no proper flushing, no proper jump-to-bottom)

        @{b}*@{ub} now dialog windows will automatically be activated when
          "DIALOG" is select for an user for whom a window already
          exists

        @{b}*@{ub} removed AmiTCP dependancy due to time() from net.lib. Now has
          it's own, even faster time() implementation using
          timer.device's GetSysTime()

@{b}Version 2.11@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} fixed word-wrap bug

        @{b}*@{ub} added "CLFT Auto Close Window" option

        @{b}*@{ub} several internal cleanups

@{b}Version 2.12 (not released)@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} fixed CLFT Receive abort bug

        @{b}*@{ub} added internal text commands "/PING nick", "/QUERY nick",
          "/AWAY <text>" and "/SEND nick" as shortcuts for the
          equivalent GUI operations

@{b}Version 2.13@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} fixed CLFT Receive accessing the wrong SocketBase

@{b}Version 2.14 (not released)@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} added regular quit operation including a preference
          definition for the default quit reason string if clchatgui is
          closed by close gadget, rexx command or CX exchange.  /QUIT
          now causes CLChatGUI to terminate itself.

        @{b}*@{ub} added version query. Syntax is "/VERSION user", version
