          querying the server version.

        @{b}*@{ub} added proper error returns for wrong parameters with the
          internal text commands.

        @{b}*@{ub} added Auto-Away capability, setting the user automatically
          /AWAY after X minutes of inactivity.

        @{b}*@{ub} cleaned up User listview refresh. Now refreshes less
          frequently and keeps the previous selection state upon list
          changes. Now sorted alphabetically and by user state.

        @{b}*@{ub} the clft send file requester now no longer rejects icon files.

@{b}Version 2.15@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} now quits with message "Changing Server" when changing server
          using the "Change Server" menu item.

        @{b}*@{ub} updated the built-in default server list.

@{b}Version 2.16@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} fixed auto-away timeout to not be reset by input done in
          dialog windows.

@{b}Version 2.17@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} Auto-Away has now a checkmark for turning it on/off.

        @{b}*@{ub} added auto away warning message.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added Auto-Unaway upon message entering.

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed options window cycle chain.

        @{b}*@{ub} added a reset handler to gracefully terminate the server link
