        @{b}*@{ub} now the CLFT process check MUI events more regularly, and
          outputs current cps in the gauge display.

        @{b}*@{ub} no more AWAY respone for VERSION query replies.

@{b}Version 2.18 (Release Version of 2.17)@{ub}
@{b}Version 2.19@{ub}
