        @{b}*@{ub} added VERSION request button to the user listview.

        @{b}*@{ub} the user listview buttons are now using the tiny MUI font.

        @{b}*@{ub} now dialog windows have a input string history, too.

        @{b}*@{ub} fixed automatic string gadget activation when clicking into
