        @{b}*@{ub} "Send files" from dialog windows didn't worked correctly.

        @{b}*@{ub} various internal fixes.

@{b}Version 2.21 (internal only)@{ub}
@{b}Version 2.22@{ub}
        @{b}*@{ub} added support for ircII formating codes: CTRL-B, CTRL-_ and
          CTRL-V. You need to turn of Input Filtering in IControl Prefs
          to use these.

        @{b}*@{ub} now, the CLFT incoming requester will also appear on the right
